Ernest U. SCHROETER, Trustee in Bankruptcy of U. S. Guaranty Corporation, et al., Appellant, v. E. H. ALLEN et al., Appellees. No. 7144. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Jan. 15, 1934.

Before WILBUR, SAWTELLE, ' and GARRECHT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; .mandate forthwith.
